query:
SELECT DISTINCT s.registrationNumber, s.fullName, se.subjectId, sub.name as subjectName, se.userId
FROM students s
INNER JOIN subjectEnrollments se ON se.studentId = s.id
INNER JOIN subjects sub ON sub.id = se.subjectId
LIMIT 5;
